{"tid":1706153,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發］等等下午兩點有民記","createTime":"2019-11-11T04:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T04:42:09.000Z","uid":84620,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"437eb97c71c9863566c0bab1f24c57958c53f7ac","tid":1706153,"uid":84620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:22:46.000Z","msg":"各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n緊急採訪通知<br />\n<br />\n因應昨天晚上「八區開花」及今天早上「黎明行動」而出現的各區警暴情況，民間記者會將作出有關回應。現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年11月11日（星期一)<br />\n時間：下午2 時<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，如有查詢可向金先生查詢。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019年11月11日<br />\n<br />\nDear members of the press,<br />\n<br />\nRe: Invitation to an Emergency Press Conference<br />\n <br />\nThe Citizens&rsquo; Press Conference will be holding an emergency press conference to give response to the serial events of anti-human behaviour by the police with regards to the protests on the streets from yesterday evening onwards overnight and in the morning today.<br />\n<br />\nWe hereby cordially invite your organisation to attend our press conference. The details of the event are as follows:<br />\n  <br />\nDate: 11 Nov 2019<br />\nTime: 2:00 PM<br />\n<br />\nEmail: kim@citizenspc.org<br />\n <br />\nShould you have any further questions, please do not hesitate to contact our representative with the information as stated above.  Thank you for your kind attention.<br />\n <br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\nCitizens&rsquo; Press Conference"},{"pid":"3144bca8adef98609e5f4e197b8434852254dcfc","tid":1706153,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c6cfe924ed9d14e17407ebb61315df3e5fab1b","tid":1706153,"uid":268131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:24:30.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒記者同民記手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a70682d6685d9866ebe15d4f7d16a3fa16bd56","tid":1706153,"uid":268131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a9ae5edc462b7cc88c0d7b620bc67d48023a77","tid":1706153,"uid":84620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:28:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c17e22eb1d7605791373bd8496b2a1b451726ad2","tid":1706153,"uid":84620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:28:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9fa2356131479bff0212651fabfcee8de1dc54e","tid":1706153,"uid":84620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f44798e722827b83cbed393dfb4af12ef5c45ee1","tid":1706153,"uid":182197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"好波<br />\n要早過4點，唔好俾曱甴先發制人"},{"pid":"4a2c1dbc5673d67a87c9e85d151a6824254a1a22","tid":1706153,"uid":65439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T04:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 民記都要小心 好危"},{"pid":"658c9882c997c4c2733c5b34a78eec99c362092f","tid":170